      <title>特朗普与斯塔默就职以来首次通话讨论贸易问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-and-starmer-discuss-trade-on-first-call-since-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相凯尔·斯塔默和美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在特朗普重返白宫后的首次通话中讨论了贸易和中东问题。他们还同意“尽快会面”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-and-starmer-discuss-trade-on-first-call-since-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 21:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙难民僵局考验以色列停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/israel-s-ceasefire-deals-face-test-with-impasse-on-gaza-refugees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列与黎巴嫩及加沙地带的停火协议因致命暴力事件以及与哈马斯就以色列人质命运的争端而面临压力，这加大了国际社会维持协议执行的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/israel-s-ceasefire-deals-face-test-with-impasse-on-gaza-refugees</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 19:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西亚尔托称卢比奥承诺美国将重新审查对匈牙利的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/rubio-pledges-us-review-of-hungary-penalties-szijjarto-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国外交部长彼得·西亚尔托在与美国总统举行会谈后表示，美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥承诺将审查拜登政府对匈牙利实施的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/rubio-pledges-us-review-of-hungary-penalties-szijjarto-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:56:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦总理提醒美国在格陵兰争端中保持强大联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/danish-premier-reminds-us-of-strong-alliance-amid-greenland-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统对格陵兰岛提出更高要求后，丹麦首相表示，美国应该记住，这个北欧国家在美国领导的战争中失去了军队，并且一直支持其大伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/danish-premier-reminds-us-of-strong-alliance-amid-greenland-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因移民争端对哥伦比亚征收关税和制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-slaps-tariffs-travel-ban-on-colombia-in-migrant-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在哥伦比亚左翼总统拒绝允许两架载有被驱逐移民的军用飞机降落几个小时后，唐纳德·特朗普总统对哥伦比亚实施了关税和制裁，以惩罚美国盟友哪怕只是部分违背他的移民目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/trump-slaps-tariffs-travel-ban-on-colombia-in-migrant-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:41:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚拒绝遣返航班 特朗普计划受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-rejects-deportation-flights-in-setback-for-trump-s-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴西谴责美国对待戴着手铐和脚镣的移民的政策后，哥伦比亚将拒绝来自美国的驱逐航班，这给唐纳德·特朗普总统的计划带来了复杂性，并与墨西哥和危地马拉的合作接受形成了鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-rejects-deportation-flights-in-setback-for-trump-s-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:14:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称与卢旺达结盟的叛军逼近刚果重要城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/un-says-rwanda-aligned-rebels-close-in-on-key-city-in-congo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维和部队负责人周日在联合国安理会紧急会议上向安理会成员表示，刚果民主共和国叛军在邻国卢旺达军队的协助下，正在逼近矿产资源丰富地区的一座重要城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/un-says-rwanda-aligned-rebels-close-in-on-key-city-in-congo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 18:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员称特朗普终止对伊朗目标的安全保护是错误的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/gop-senators-say-trump-is-wrong-to-end-security-for-iran-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名共和党参议员敦促唐纳德·特朗普总统撤销终止为其前助手提供政府安全细节的决定，因为这些助手面临伊朗对美国在 2020 年杀害一名伊朗高级指挥官的报复风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/gop-senators-say-trump-is-wrong-to-end-security-for-iran-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 17:00:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶降雨有助于扑灭火灾，但也带来山体滑坡风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/los-angeles-is-getting-good-rain-yet-faces-risk-of-landslides</link>
      <description><![CDATA[干旱的洛杉矶迎来了数月来的第一场降雨——潮湿的天气有助于扑灭野火，但也带来了山体滑坡的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/los-angeles-is-getting-good-rain-yet-faces-risk-of-landslides</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 14:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世卫组织总干事称苏丹达尔富尔医院袭击事件造成约 70 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/urgent-some-70-people-killed-in-attack-on-hospital-in-sudan-s-darfur-region-who-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——世界卫生组织负责人周日表示，苏丹被围困的城市法希尔唯一一家正常运营的医院遭到袭击，造成约 70 人死亡，这是最近几天该非洲国家内战升级过程中发生的一系列袭击事件之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/urgent-some-70-people-killed-in-attack-on-hospital-in-sudan-s-darfur-region-who-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 04:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
